          </p>
          <p>
            Roll each hard-cooked egg in flour to coat; place on sausage patty
            and shape sausage around egg. Dip each into beaten egg; coat with
            bread crumbs to cover completely. Place on ungreased cookie sheet.
          </p>
          <p>
            Bake 35 minutes or until sausage is thoroughly cooked and no longer
            pink near egg.
